Yash Dayal bowling to Angkrish Raghuvanshi, THAT'S A STUNNER!  good length ball, pitching on off stump, Angkrish Raghuvanshi leans across and chips the ball nonchalantly over mid-wicket, looking for a boundary. Most fielders would struggle, but Green isn't most fielders. He displays exceptional athleticism, back-tracking with his eyes glued to the ball. Two wickets in the over, and RCB are absolutely buzzing to end the powerplay on a high! Faf du Plessis, the skipper, can't help but crack a wide smile. That was a special catch!
